Title: Best long term cure for depression
Description: Depression is a common complaint in the Western world. Its societal cost is huge. This worldwide collaborative effort aims to find the best treatment available: psychological, biological, alternative or any combinations. We look at long term healing: at 12 months. In times of financial restraints, it makes sense to also find the most cost/effective treatment available today.
Contributors: Frederik Feys
Tags: depression

Best long term cure for depression
Depression is a common complaint in the Western world. Its societal cost is huge. This worldwide collaborative effort aims to find the best treatment available: psychological, biological, alternative or any combinations. We look at long term healing: at 12 months. In times of financial restraints, it makes sense to also find the most cost/effective treatment available today.
